{"id":110,"ayahs":[{"number":14,"arabic":"وَمِنَ ٱلَّذِينَ قَالُوٓا۟ إِنَّا نَصَٰرَىٰٓ أَخَذْنَا مِيثَٰقَهُمْ فَنَسُوا۟ حَظًّۭا مِّمَّا ذُكِّرُوا۟ بِهِۦ فَأَغْرَيْنَا بَيْنَهُمُ ٱلْعَدَاوَةَ وَٱلْبَغْضَآءَ إِلَىٰ يَوْمِ ٱلْقِيَٰمَةِ ۚ وَسَوْفَ يُنَبِّئُهُمُ ٱللَّهُ بِمَا كَانُوا۟ يَصْنَعُونَ","translation":"And [likewise,] from those who say, \"Behold, we are Christians.\" We have accepted a solemn pledge: and they, too, have forgotten much of what they had been told to bear in mind - wherefore We have given rise among them to enmity and hatred, [to last] until Resurrection Day: and in time God will cause them to understand what they have contrived.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/683.mp3","surahId":5,"words":[{"id":16353,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمِنَ","translation":"এবং মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/005_014_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":16354,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_014_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":16355,"position":3,"arabic":"قَالُوٓا۟","translation":"(যারা) বলেছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/005_014_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":16356,"position":4,"arabic":"إِنَّا","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/005_014_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":16357,"position":5,"arabic":"نَصَـٰرَىٰٓ","translation":"খ্রিষ্টান\"","audioUrl":"wbw/005_014_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":16358,"position":6,"arabic":"أَخَذْنَا","translation":"আমরা নিয়েছিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/005_014_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":16359,"position":7,"arabic":"مِيثَـٰقَهُمْ","translation":"অংগীকার তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/005_014_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":16360,"position":8,"arabic":"فَنَسُوا۟","translation":"কিন্তু তারা ভুলে গেলো","audioUrl":"wbw/005_014_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":16361,"position":9,"arabic":"حَظًّۭا","translation":"এক অংশ","audioUrl":"wbw/005_014_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":16362,"position":10,"arabic":"مِّمَّا","translation":"তা হতে 